# NestJS standards — {{WORKSPACE_NAME}}

> **Purpose**: The authoritative engineering-conventions document for every NestJS repo in this workspace. Naming, auth, persistence, migrations, tests, module layout — **how we write NestJS here**, not architecture (that's `platform.md`).
> **Last Updated**: {{DATE}}
