This document is populated by reading the actual code in the workspace's NestJS repos. Every convention below names what already exists — not what the plugin thinks NestJS "should" do. A repo on Prisma doesn't get TypeORM rules; an app with a custom JWT strategy doesn't get Passport rules.

**Stable section anchors (§1–§9) are cited by number from implementer and reviewer agents.** Do not renumber existing sections; you may add §10+.

